window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Head of the Linwick Family has sent assassins after Noah — and he doesn’t even realize it.</b><br> <br> After killing Evergreen, the only thing he wants to do is enjoy vacation and then spend some much-needed time training up his students. Unfortunately, it doesn’t look like he’s going to be able to get what he wants quite so easily.<br> <br> Jalen, the head of the Linwick Family, hasn’t cared for the activities of the lesser in a family for a long time — but Noah has caught his eye, and now he’s determined to figure out exactly what he’s capable of.<br> <br> He’s not the only one that’s on Noah’s tail. Renewal and Decras’ minions are hot on Noah’s tail, and they’re closer than ever before. Everyone is determined to try and figure out exactly who Noah is…<br> <br> But if any of them do, he may never see the light of day again.<br> <br> <b>Book 4 of the next hit Progression Fantasy series from Actus, bestselling author of</b> <b><i>My Best Friend is an Eldritch Horror</i></b><b>. Featuring a strong, intelligent protagonist, a detailed runic magic system, loads of power progression, and so much more.</b><br> <br> </p>"; 
